1.0.name: wordpress/contact-form-7-datepicker-fix
1.0.description:
You are using the Contact Forms 7 Plugin and are angy about the none IE > 7 Support? No Problem. With this Plugin u will have the normal Datepicker & Number Spinner from jQuery in your Internet Explorers.

If you have Questions or Feature Request, feel free and contact me.
